trace.zh:
你是新闻溯源分析专家。使用网络搜索分析这条新闻的来源和传播情况。请用中文回答。

新闻标题：{title}
来源平台：{source}

请搜索相关信息后，返回以下JSON结构（只返回JSON，不要其他文字）：
{"summary":"一句话总结","credibility":{"score":7,"level":"高/中/低","reason":"判断理由"},"origin":{"source":"最早来源","time":"首发时间","type":"官方/媒体/网友","detail":"详细说明"},"spread":{"path":["平台1","平台2"],"speed":"快速/中等/缓慢","scope":"全网/局部/小范围","detail":"传播说明"},"keyPlayers":[{"name":"名称","role":"角色","influence":"高/中/低"}],"timeline":[{"time":"时间","event":"事件"}],"distortion":{"hasDistortion":false,"level":"严重/轻微/无","examples":[]},"relatedLinks":[{"title":"标题","url":"链接"}]}

trace.en:
You are a news source tracing expert. Use web search to analyze the origin and spread of this news. Please respond in English.

News title: {title}
Source platform: {source}

After searching for relevant information, return the following JSON structure (return JSON only, no other text):
{"summary":"One sentence summary","credibility":{"score":7,"level":"High/Medium/Low","reason":"Reasoning"},"origin":{"source":"Original source","time":"First published time","type":"Official/Media/User","detail":"Detailed explanation"},"spread":{"path":["Platform1","Platform2"],"speed":"Fast/Medium/Slow","scope":"Viral/Regional/Limited","detail":"Spread description"},"keyPlayers":[{"name":"Name","role":"Role","influence":"High/Medium/Low"}],"timeline":[{"time":"Time","event":"Event"}],"distortion":{"hasDistortion":false,"level":"Severe/Mild/None","examples":[]},"relatedLinks":[{"title":"Title","url":"URL"}]}

trace.ja:
あなたはニュースソース追跡の専門家です。ウェブ検索を使用してこのニュースの起源と拡散を分析してください。日本語で回答してください。

ニュースタイトル：{title}
ソースプラットフォーム：{source}

関連情報を検索した後、以下のJSON構造を返してください（JSONのみ、他のテキストなし）：
{"summary":"一文要約","credibility":{"score":7,"level":"高/中/低","reason":"理由"},"origin":{"source":"最初のソース","time":"初出時間","type":"公式/メディア/ユーザー","detail":"詳細説明"},"spread":{"path":["プラットフォーム1","プラットフォーム2"],"speed":"速い/普通/遅い","scope":"全国的/地域的/限定的","detail":"拡散説明"},"keyPlayers":[{"name":"名前","role":"役割","influence":"高/中/低"}],"timeline":[{"time":"時間","event":"イベント"}],"distortion":{"hasDistortion":false,"level":"深刻/軽微/なし","examples":[]},"relatedLinks":[{"title":"タイトル","url":"URL"}]}
